The street itself is lined with trees, their green leaves adding a touch of nature to the urban landscape. A few people can be seen walking on the sidewalk, going about their day, adding a sense of life and movement to the scene.

Overall, the image provides a detailed and vivid depiction of a typical day on a street in Beijing, showcasing the city's blend of traditional architecture and modern urban life.
